<HistoricalDocument xmlns="http://example.com/historicaldocument">
  <Metadata>
    <Language>German</Language>
    <WritingDirection>ltr</WritingDirection>
    <PhysicalDescription>Parchment, single folio side, good condition.</PhysicalDescription>
    <Description>List of names and titles, possibly related to ecclesiastical appointments or records from Königsfelden Abbey.</Description>
    <Script>Latin</Script>
  </Metadata>
  <Page>
    <Header>
      <PageNumber>93</PageNumber>
    </Header>
    <Body>
      <Paragraph>
        <Line>us dem land ze</Line>
        <Line>magglenburg</Line>
        <Line>Cūrat hobe <Emphasis type="underline">ritt</Emphasis></Line>
        <Line>Dietrich liebzow</Line>
        <Line>peter ein <Emphasis type="underline">barfuͦb</Emphasis> <Emphasis type="underline">priest</Emphasis></Line>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph>
        <Line>us Luttringen</Line>
        <Line>Jokob von <Emphasis type="underline">harckurt</Emphasis> <Emphasis type="underline">rit</Emphasis></Line>
        <Line>Desiderius <Emphasis type="underline">von</Emphasis> <Emphasis type="underline">mirēcurt</Emphasis> <Emphasis type="underline">priest</Emphasis></Line>
        <Line>Cola von <Emphasis type="underline">bayen</Emphasis> <Emphasis type="underline">sin</Emphasis> <Emphasis type="underline">knecht</Emphasis></Line>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph>
        <Line>us <Emphasis type="underline">holsten</Emphasis> land</Line>
        <Line>Jakob <Emphasis type="underline">velling</Emphasis></Line>
        <Line>Hans <Emphasis type="underline">rudbeck</Emphasis></Line>
        <Line>Heinrich <Emphasis type="underline">lang</Emphasis></Line>
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph>
        <Line>von <Emphasis type="underline">strosburg</Emphasis></Line>
        <Line>Hans von <Emphasis type="underline">benfelt</Emphasis> ein <Emphasis type="underline">priest</Emphasis></Line>
        <Line>fant <Emphasis type="underline">johans</Emphasis> <Emphasis type="underline">ordens</Emphasis></Line>
      </Paragraph>
    </Body>
  </Page>
</HistoricalDocument>
